data.description: Welcome home! Charming 2 bedroom, 1 bath ranch in the coveted Oakwood Neighborhood. Step inside to discover the warmth of bamboo flooring that graces the inviting living room, creating a welcoming ambiance. The adjacent kitchen is a delight, featuring sleek stainless-steel appliances complemented by a stylish tile backsplash. A modern full bath adds to the appeal, accompanying two bedrooms, including a generously sized primary bedroom. For added convenience, a stackable washer & dryer complete the main floor. Venture downstairs to a meticulously kept full basement, offering abundant storage space. The fully fenced backyard is expansive & offers an ideal area for pets to roam while you unwind on the back deck. Completing the scene, a detached two-car garage not only adds convenience but also provides extra storage space. Don't wait, schedule a showing today!
